vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">该款产品为珠型藤茶，原料采自端午节后成熟的藤茶嫩叶。茶禅一味藤茶礼盒为每盒有4个50G精美铁盒装，分为小袋包装，取用均十分方便。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130730/20130730145146_74217.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130730/20130730145146_74217.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130726/20130726171353_86690.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130726/20130726171353_86690.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">富硒藤茶含有丰富的黄酮、氨基酸、维生素和人体必需的微量元素。依据中国预防医学科学院营养与食品卫生所营养成分分析结果，每</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">100g</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">产品水分</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">9.4g,</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">热量为</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">291</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">千卡，主要营养素蛋白质</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">20.4g</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、脂肪</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">0.8g</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、胡萝卜素</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">5.23mg</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、维生素</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">E6.32mg</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、铁</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">10.1mg</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、锌</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">1.58mg</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、钙</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">411.3mg</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、铜</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">0.67mg</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、镁</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">121.6mg</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">、硒</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">10.62&mu;g</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">，含有丰富的黄铜类化合物。与《食物成分表》中茶叶类相比，其营养成分较齐全，优于一般茶叶，尤其是<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">黄铜类化合物和硒的含量远高</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">于绿茶和花茶。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">金祈藤茶每</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">100</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克金祈藤茶当中含有</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">10.31g</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">的植物黄酮、</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">820</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&mu;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">g</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">的微量元素&ldquo;硒&rdquo;，同时含有人体必需的</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">18</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">种微量元素和</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">22</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">种氨基酸。富硒藤茶富含硒，元素符号为Se，它是人体所必需的微量元素。硒在人体内无法合成，所以要满足人体对硒的需求，就需要每天补充硒。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">藤茶中黄酮类化合物</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">，其主体物质为二氢杨梅素</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">，它对自由基的清除率高达</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">73.3%</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">～</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">91.5%</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">，可减轻机体内氧化损伤</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">。藤茶还能减轻动物肝组织的变性和坏死程度。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130730/20130730114302_69314.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130730/20130730114302_69314.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">取茶：5&mdash;15克</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;冲泡：85度左右开水冲泡，以500毫升水为宜，加盖闷泡5分钟。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 酌饮：</span><b><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(0, 153, 0); font-size: 14px;\">保健量</span></b><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>：</strong>15&mdash;25克/天，<b><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\"><strong>食疗量</strong></span></b></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(0, 102, 0); font-size: 14px;\"><strong>：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">30克以上/天</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"750\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130726/20130726172406_12570.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130726/20130726172406_12570.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201609/thumb_img/7_thumb_G_1475091808519.jpg', 'images/201609/goods_img/7_G_1475091808678.jpg', 'images/201609/source_img/7_G_1475091808772.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '5', '1475091808', '100', '0', '0', '1', '0', '1', '0', '1475866626', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
