/themes/xipinhui/images/product/img0201.jpg\" alt=\"人生多吃点好的 就少吃点差的\" original=\"themes/xipinhui/images/product/img0201.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\" /><img src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/themes/xipinhui/images/product/img1125.jpg\" alt=\"三不承诺 7S标准\" original=\"themes/xipinhui/images/product/img1125.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\" /><img alt=\"健康食品金字塔\" original=\"themes/xipinhui/images/product/img0502.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/themes/xipinhui/images/product/img0502.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\" />\r\n<div class=\"goods_desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805170500_74991.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805170500_74991.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805162021_29874.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805162021_29874.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">葛根，为豆科植物野葛，是中国南方一些省区的一种常食蔬菜，其味甘凉可口。中国自古就有&ldquo;南葛北参&rdquo;的说法，在古代葛根被列入&ldquo;官药&rdquo;，有些品种还被当作贡品服务于帝王将相家。葛根是我国卫生部批准的药食兼备的植物，是老少皆宜的名贵滋补品，其素有&ldquo;亚洲人参&rdquo;、&ldquo;长寿人参&ldquo;之美誉。葛根全身是宝,在我国有悠久的应用历史,连葛藤、葛叶、葛花 都有应用之法。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805162144_16227.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805162144_16227.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></div>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">葛花，紫红色，葛谷，形如豆荚。葛花在立秋后，当花未全开放时，采其花蕾，去其枝叶，自然晒干。本款葛花茶是采用天然野葛花及多种名贵中药材和大别山野山茶精制而成的，据《神农本草经》、《千金方》、《本草纲目》记载，葛花具有特殊的</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">解酒醒脾</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">功效，故民间有</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">千杯不醉野葛花</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">之说。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">葛花茶也因此被称为&ldquo;解酒 神茶&rdquo;，因为葛花、葛根具有很强的解酒功能，另据《中药大辞典》评述，葛花、葛根不仅有解酒功效，还具有清热解毒、养颜护肤之功效，同时，还对缓解高血压、冠心病、心绞痛、突发性耳聋有一定作用。葛花茶还可治肠风下血、男性前列腺炎等。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805163043_18640.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805163043_18640.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 野生的干燥葛花花蕾呈不规则的扁长圆形或略成扁肾形，葛花茶气味清香、汁味醇厚甘鲜、浓郁悠长、不加任何添加剂,是迄今为为止最有效的纯天然解酒植物。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805163123_71556.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805163123_71556.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;世界硒都&mdash;&mdash;湖北恩施毗邻神龙架，地处武夷山脉，海拔高，</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">属于亚热带山原型季风性湿润气候。其特点是光热充足、雨量充沛、春夏多雨、 秋冬干旱、无霜期长、冬无严寒、四季湿和，小气候明显， 昼夜温差大，地处偏僻，无任何工业污染。该地为全球唯一探明的独立硒矿床，世界最大的富硒生态圈，突然中富含优质硒资源，该地的深山老林中盛产各种野生山珍药材，包括野生葛根</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805164127_15356.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805164127_15356.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;硒品汇该款葛花茶礼盒为4小盒组成，每小盒包装葛花茶为3g/袋*10袋。于喝酒前10分钟泡上一小袋，可以在胃部形成一层保护膜，大大降低酒精对人体伤害和增加酒量，在酒后喝上一杯解酒神茶葛花茶，可以迅速促进酒精的分解，是喝酒应酬着必备的护体神器，是送给客户朋友家人的不二之选。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805164848_85354.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805164848_85354.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805165022_15337.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805165022_15337.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201609/thumb_img/11_thumb_G_1475092360054.jpg', 'images/201609/goods_img/11_G_1475092360580.jpg', 'images/201609/source_img/11_G_1475092360277.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '1', '1475092360', '100', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1475092441', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
