in: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; width: 750px;\"><img src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/themes/xipinhui/images/product/img0201.jpg\" alt=\"人生多吃点好的 就少吃点差的\" original=\"themes/xipinhui/images/product/img0201.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\" /><img src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/themes/xipinhui/images/product/img1125.jpg\" alt=\"三不承诺 7S标准\" original=\"themes/xipinhui/images/product/img1125.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\" /><img alt=\"健康食品金字塔\" original=\"themes/xipinhui/images/product/img0502.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/themes/xipinhui/images/product/img0502.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block;\" />\r\n<div class=\"goods_desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141116/20141116215356_53898.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141116/20141116215356_53898.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141221/20141221233255_44718.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141221/20141221233255_44718.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141221/20141221233454_72039.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141221/20141221233454_72039.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 24px; font-family: \'arial verdana 宋体\';\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;我们均在</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 213, 255);\"><strong>发货当天</strong></span>从大酒坛</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">灌装进桶，建议收到以后</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">长期储存的朋友</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">换装坛子保存。即饮的客户2个月内可以不换坛子。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141225/20141225101958_27713.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141225/20141225101958_27713.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610185001_49110.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610185001_49110.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 众所周知，酒精对肝脏的伤害尤为严重，这也使得很多人一方面贪恋美酒的甘爽另一方面却顾忌健康的损伤。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;很多科学试验证明，天然硒有着十分显著的保肝护肝功能，可以有效地防止各类肝脏疾病发生。因此，以富含</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">天然硒的苞谷和山泉水为主要原料的富硒苞谷酒不但从根本上解决了喝酒伤肝的问题，更让饮酒成为一件于身于心皆有益的乐事。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610185041_49542.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610185041_49542.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;我们硒品汇的富硒贡酒来自从原料到生产均为来自</span><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">地处北纬30度的武陵山区&mdash;&mdash;世界硒都湖北恩施。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">我原料基地和生产基地均处于</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">的海拔约1100米（一般内地城市象北京海拔高度在20~60米），和神农架相距100多公里，同属于武陵山系。李琼《山路十入弯》唱的就是我们当地的风景、青歌赛上原生态组合&quot;撒尔嗬&quot;就是我们镇上地地道道的土家人，这会儿大家对我们这里有印象了吧。我们当地80岁的老人下地干活是常见的。2005年前我们这里的医院都没有肿瘤科，这足以说明我们当地的生活环境和水质好了。（土地和水都富硒，硒是抗癌和长寿的重要元素）</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610185947_63257.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610185947_63257.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610190132_45727.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610190132_45727.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: \'microsoft yahei\'; font-size: 18px; line-height: 27px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610190436_37479.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20140610/20140610190436_37479.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201610/thumb_img/16_thumb_G_1475865927850.jpg', 'images/201610/goods_img/16_G_1475865927938.jpg', 'images/201610/source_img/16_G_1475865927866.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '1', '1475865927', '100', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1475866613', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
