g: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; width: 750px;\"><br />\r\n<div class=\"goods_desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010143406_89032.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010143406_89032.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010143427_92357.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010143427_92357.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;硒品汇的珍硒贡米<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px;\">米粒晶莹剔透，饭熟揭盖时，饭粒油身色亮，一股箬叶（棕子）香味扑面而来，四处飘溢，米饭柔软、甘滑，香味浓，口感佳，令宾客食欲大增。</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(0, 153, 0);\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725182935_74917.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725182935_74917.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&ldquo;木龙寨&rdquo;珍硒贡米，曾在清朝乾隆年间，本县文人志士，广传家乡土特产品，将木龙镇地产优质大米选送为宫廷纳贡佳品，&ldquo;木龙寨&rdquo;贡米因此而得名。 硒品汇富硒贡米为严格按照有机食品栽培技术要求规范种植，采用先进的环保加工工艺生产出的有机米。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px;\">因产品富含天然硒、锌和多种氨基酸、蛋白质等微量元素，常食&ldquo;木龙寨&rdquo;贡米。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">按照中国营养学会提出的每人每天硒食入量为0.05-0.4毫克的指标，我们所食用的普通大米硒含量仅0.02毫克/公斤，远远不能满足人体需求。通过吃天然富硒米饭补硒是当今世界公认的经济、实用、有效的补硒途径。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010143818_39879.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010143818_39879.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 硒品汇<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px;\">&ldquo;木龙寨&rdquo;富硒贡米产于宣恩县沙道沟镇的木龙寨，<span style=\"color: rgb(100, 69, 29); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">是一个远离城市的小山村，</span>山水奇特秀丽，山上森林茂密，雨量充沛，四季阳光充足，气候怡人，自然环境纯净，土壤富含硒、锌、铁等多种微量元量，以盛产水稻为主，素有&ldquo;千丘田&rdquo;之称。<span style=\"color: rgb(100, 69, 29); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">特别是恩施土壤天然含硒，水稻吸收土壤中硒元素后，通过光合作用，转化成人体可以吸收的有机硒</span><span style=\"color: rgb(161, 161, 161); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 69, 29);\">&nbsp;，具有非常高的营养养生价值</span><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 69, 29);\">。</span></span>这里自古产名米，出贡品。</span><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010143924_80063.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010143924_80063.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp;硒品汇所售富硒贡米现在为有机转化阶段产品，<span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">严格按照有机大米的质量管理体系，严密跟踪从选种、播种、生长、采集、加工、包装、贮藏、运输全过程。</span>包装材料也完全遵循有机食品的要求，内包装为真空包装，便于存放；外</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">包装有有机转化期认证标识和富硒食品标志，保证食品质量，做到真正的放心米。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">5kg</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">实惠装大米最适合家有老人儿童的家庭选用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010144121_58047.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141010/20141010144121_58047.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp; 现有市场上的富硒大米都是通过在含有大、中、微量元素的叶面肥中加入微量元素硒，在水稻破口至抽穗期进行叶面喷施，通过作物叶面吸收，提高硒的含量。&ldquo;木龙寨&rdquo;富硒贡米，原粮基地选在绿色无污染的生态恩施州，选种优良品种，选用纯天然的高硒矿粉通过土壤补硒，植被根部缓慢持续吸收，来增加产品的硒含量，更健更有机更环保。</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">富硒贡米除了和一般大米一样，含碳水化合物75%左右，蛋白质7%-8%，脂肪1.3%-1. 8%，并含有丰富的B族维生素成份外，还</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">富含多种维生素、矿物质、氨基酸和微量元素，其中硒的含量是普通大米的8-10倍蛋白质含量是普通大米的12</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">倍。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130806/20130806142230_46094.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130806/20130806142230_46094.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130806/20130806154816_24878.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130806/20130806154816_24878.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201610/thumb_img/19_thumb_G_1475867606781.jpg', 'images/201610/goods_img/19_G_1475867606109.jpg', 'images/201610/source_img/19_G_1475867606535.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1475867606', '100', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1475867717', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
