 0px; padding: 5px 10px; float: left; width: 324px; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">包装样式：袋装</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; width: 750px;\"><br />\r\n<div class=\"goods_desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20150117/20150117220318_39831.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20150117/20150117220318_39831.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802113718_59023.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802113718_59023.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"375\" title=\"黑色杂粮,黑类食品,黑色粮食,黑大豆,,\" alt=\"黑色杂粮,黑类食品,黑色粮食,黑大豆,,\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802113805_70232.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802113805_70232.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"416\" title=\"黑豆实物,传统品种,非转基因,,\" alt=\"黑豆实物,传统品种,非转基因,,\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802113821_82160.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802113821_82160.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;硒品汇硒大大黑豆属于农家传统品种的黄心黑豆，颗粒完整饱满，无杂质，色泽乌黑发亮，质坚硬，种皮薄而脆，<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 153, 0);\">不经过任何人工处理。</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 153, 0); font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 153, 0);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725182935_74917.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725182935_74917.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 黑豆</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">味甘，性微寒。能补肾益阴，健脾利湿，除热解毒，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">可促进胆固醇的代谢、降低血脂，预防心血管疾病</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">，可促进肠胃蠕动，预防便秘，所以是不错的减肥佳品，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">而且还有治疗风湿、抗衰老、</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">健脑益智，美容</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">等效果。具体功效有：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>1、降胆固</strong><strong>醇</strong>：</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">近年来很多研究表明，黑豆的异黄酮和卵磷脂含量特别丰富也是与关系的，这两个同样都有抗动脉硬化，降胆固醇这个作用。而且黑豆不含胆固醇，只含一种植物固醇，具有抑制人体吸收胆固醇，具有降低血液中胆固醇含量的作用。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>2</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>、补肾美容：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">豆乃肾之谷，</span><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑色正好是我们肾的本色，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">所以黑豆入肾功能多。通过肾经的充盈来间接补充我们的肝血，是肝血得到滋养以后我们的眼睛就能眼明目俏。中医认为人的肌肤，它的光泽润泽是靠我们肾气的滋养，肾气的充盈，温煦，靠肾经的滋润。我们常吃黑豆既可以补充肾气，也可以补充肾阴，从而使我们的皮肤衰老得到延缓，皱纹出现会减少。同时常吃黑豆，我们可以降低由于色素沉着引起的黄褐斑和老年斑，所以说黑豆是很好的肌肤美容之品。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>3</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>、益脾：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑豆味甘，还入脾经，所以具有健脾益气的作用。同时黑豆还可以祛水的作用，所以有些人水肿，面部红肿，长期吃黑豆都可以很好的利水作用。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>4.祛痰止喘</strong><strong>，可治咳嗽：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">对胃胀，便秘有明显疗效。</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>5</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>、抗氧化</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>，抗衰老：</strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑豆皮为黑色，含有花青素，花青素是很好的抗氧化剂来源，能清除体内自由基，尤其是在胃的酸性环境下，抗氧化效果好，滋阴养颜美容，增加肠胃蠕动。</span>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑豆中含有丰富的维生素E、VE也是一种抗氧化剂，能清除体内自由基，减少皮肤皱纹，对祛除色斑也有一定功效，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">减少皮肤</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">皱纹，达到养颜美容、保持青春的目的。</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>6、排毒减肥</strong><strong>：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑豆中粗纤维的含量达4%，超过黄豆很多，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">乌豆的美容功效之去除痘痘排毒通便作用</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">。</span></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/includes/kindeditor/php/../../../images/upload/image/20130808/20130808143853_91324.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130808/20130808143853_91324.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><img alt=\"\" original=\"/includes/kindeditor/php/../../../images/upload/image/20130808/20130808143858_42886.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130808/20130808143858_42886.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130808/20130808143917_24720.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130808/20130808143917_24720.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 硒品汇产品的基地位于世界硒都&mdash;&mdash;湖北恩施州的白杨坪乡，当地为武陵山脉，属于次高山地貌，国内罕有的富硒生态生物圈。距离硒床核心区仅20公里，为最近的天然高硒种植基地。在基地方圆数十公里内没有工厂，保证的粮食生长的环境没有污染，基地部分作物已经经过有机食品认证，为真正做到放心粮。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20150117/20150117220345_33468.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20150117/20150117220345_33468.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp;硒品汇产自</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">世界硒都的黑豆，原生态无污染，品质好</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">天然含硒。</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">外包装正规环保，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">采用环保材料制成，可回收利用。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"750\" height=\"528\" title=\"无杂粮黑豆,补肾食品,滋补食品,滋阴食品,\" alt=\"无杂粮黑豆,补肾食品,滋补食品,滋阴食品,\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802121706_47830.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802121706_47830.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">真空包装，便于存放。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725183023_34524.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725183023_34524.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;黑豆具有高蛋白、低热量的特性，蛋白质含量高达45%以上，其中优质蛋白大约比黄豆高出1/4左右，居各种豆类之首，因此也赢得了&ldquo;豆中之王&rdquo;的美誉。与蛋白质丰富的肉类相比，黑豆蛋白质含量相当于肉类（猪肉、鸡肉）的2倍，是鸡蛋的3倍，更是牛奶的12倍，因此又被誉为&ldquo;植物蛋白肉&rdquo;。每100克黑豆中含粗脂肪高达12克以上，检测发现其中含有至少19种脂肪酸，而且不饱和脂肪酸含量竟然高达80%，其中亚油酸含量就占了约55. 08%，亚油酸能防止导致动脉硬化的发生，有&ldquo;血管清道夫&rdquo;的美誉。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 黑豆还富含发现多种矿物质及微量元素，如锌、铜、镁、钼、硒、磷等，同时富含异黄酮，皂苷、黑豆色素等营养物质和多种维生素，尤其是维生素E在每百克黑豆中的含高达17.36微克，皂苷和维生素E（Vitamin E）是一种脂溶性维生素，是最主要的抗氧化剂之一。同时还能提供食物中粗纤维，促进消化，防止便秘发生。总之，黑豆就是一种高蛋白、低热量，多保健功能的黄金食品。</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img width=\"769\" height=\"1171\" title=\"黑豆食用方法,黑豆猪蹄汤,熟黑豆,黑豆粥\" alt=\"黑豆食用方法,黑豆猪蹄汤,熟黑豆,黑豆粥\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802134348_84074.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802134348_84074.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">黑豆可</span><span style=\"line-height: 26px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">做粥或汤、豆浆，也可磨粉做饼、糕等，也可做熟直接使用</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>黑豆减肥茶</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">【做法】</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">15颗干燥的黑豆放到平底锅中，干煎一下，带黑豆的表皮裂开后，将黑豆放到杯子中。然后将150毫升的水煮沸后，倒入杯中，盖上杯盖焖泡5分钟后即可饮用。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">【功效】</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">抑制脂肪的吸收。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑豆豆浆</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">【做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑豆、砂糖、水 &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;1、先将黑豆洗干净，在</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">温水中泡7-8小时，水要淹过黑豆约二到三倍高。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、待黑豆泡软，倒掉泡黑豆的水，把黑豆放入豆浆机（料理机）中。视自己的豆浆机（料理机）大小加入适量的黑豆，加水不要超过最高水位线。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;3、启用豆浆机十多分钟煮开，新鲜的黑豆浆就做好了。如果使用料理机的话打出来的就是生豆浆，要彻底煮熟了才能喝。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、大家可以按照自己的口味加入适量的糖，这样口感会更好的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">【功效】<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">黑豆浆不像黄豆性冷，喝多了也不会拉肚子，而且还有</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">降血脂、预防心血管疾病、抗氧化，延缓衰老、养颜美容，增加肠胃蠕动。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>黑豆枸杞粥</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;【做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑豆</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">100克，枸杞子3～5克，红枣5～10个，料酒、姜汁、食盐各适量，前面</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">配料加水适量，&nbsp;用急火煮沸后，改用文火熬至黑豆烂熟，即可取汤饮用，每日早、晚饮用，每次2～3杯为宜，可长期饮用。（亦可用决明子代替枸杞）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;【功效】</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">对防治眼睛疲劳、视力模糊效果更好。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;【小窍门】</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">黑豆泡的时候，会掉色，水色加深，属正常现象。如果只是洗了一下，就掉色或者泡的时候水色特深，有可能是经过染色加工。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201610/thumb_img/22_thumb_G_1475868018652.jpg', 'images/201610/goods_img/22_G_1475868018647.jpg', 'images/201610/source_img/22_G_1475868018693.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1475868018', '100', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '1475868021', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
