in: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; width: 750px;\">\r\n<div class=\"goods_desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20150118/20150118002206_78669.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20150118/20150118002206_78669.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802100554_92149.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802100554_92149.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802100702_99457.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802100702_99457.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802100806_48733.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802100806_48733.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;硒品汇天然含硒红豆</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">为农家传统品种，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(0, 153, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">干燥种子，呈矩圆形，两端圆钝或平截，，种皮赤红色，平滑有光泽，种脐位于侧缘上端，白色，不显著突出，亦不凹陷。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 153, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"596\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130726/20130726135629_78160.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130726/20130726135629_78160.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"502\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725194519_15274.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725194519_15274.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 硒品汇产品的基地位于湖北恩施州的白杨坪乡，当地为武陵山脉，属于次高山地貌，国内罕有的富硒生态生物圈。距离硒床核心区仅20公里，为最近的天然高硒种植基地。在基地方圆数十公里内没有工厂，保证的粮食生长的环境没有污染，基地部分作物已经经过有机食品认证，为真正做到放心粮。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20150118/20150118002256_92349.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20150118/20150118002256_92349.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">产自世界硒都的天然含硒红小豆，原生态无污染，品质好</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">天然含硒。</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">外包装正规环保，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">采用环保材料制成，可回收利用。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802110259_32715.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130802/20130802110259_32715.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">真空包装，便于存放。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725183023_34524.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130725/20130725183023_34524.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;在每100克的赤小豆中，含蛋白质20.7克，脂肪0.5克，碳水化合物58克，粗纤维4.6克，钙67毫克，铁5.2毫克，还有磷，维生素B1、B2、烟酸以及皂草甙等营养物质。&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130808/20130808151322_52736.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130808/20130808151322_52736.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 赤豆可整粒食用，一般用于煮饭、煮粥、做赤豆汤或冰棍、雪糕之类，也可用于菜肴有&ldquo;红豆排骨汤&rdquo;等。由于赤豆淀粉含量较高，蒸后呈粉沙性，而且有独特的香气，故常用来做成豆沙，以供各种糕团面点的陷料。赤豆还可发制赤豆芽，食用同绿豆芽。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>红豆鲤鱼汤&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">【做法】</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">取赤小豆1斤，活鲤鱼1条(重1斤以上)，同放锅内，加水2000～3000毫升清炖，至赤小豆烂透为止。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><b>红豆粥</b></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">【做法】</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">赤豆30-50克，水煮至半熟，放入粳米100克同煮粥，以淡食为宜，加白糖调味食用亦可。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">红绿百合羹&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;【做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">绿豆、红豆、百合各20克浸半小时，以大火煮滚后收至慢火至豆熟，加入适量的糖或盐，咸食甜食皆可。</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201610/thumb_img/24_thumb_G_1475868311636.jpg', 'images/201610/goods_img/24_G_1475868311209.jpg', 'images/201610/source_img/24_G_1475868311849.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1475868311', '100', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '0', '1475868313', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
