ing: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; width: 750px;\"><br />\r\n<div class=\"goods_desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141124/20141124010238_20148.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141124/20141124010238_20148.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\">硒品汇所售</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">脱水山药生片来自神秘北纬30度，平均海拔1200米的武陵山区腹地&mdash;&mdash;素有&ldquo;绿色植物王国&rdquo;和&ldquo;世界硒都&rdquo;之称的湖北恩施。以平均海拔1200米的种植基地有机优质米山药为原料，经过剥皮，低温脱水制成，不含任何添加剂、防腐剂，无硫，保留了山药的原色、原味、原营养，是我们日常养生膳食的优质食材。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141124/20141124002345_10561.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141124/20141124002345_10561.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></span></div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">硒品汇所售的天然含硒脱水蔬菜</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; font-size: 14px;\">主产区为硒都利川县团堡镇，该地生态条件好，平均海拔1100米，林业用地面积420.34万亩，占国土总面积的60.87%。森林面积334.39万亩，森林覆盖率55.71%。项目实施地点的团堡镇地处东经109&deg;03&prime;～109&deg;18&prime;、北纬30&deg;12&prime;～30&deg;34&prime;这条地球的神秘文化带上，境内喀斯特地貌尤为突出。东有石板岭为利川、恩施两市天然界山；西有金字山突兀高耸，形似玉笔，为利川八大景之一；南有马鬃岭，形似鬃毛披散的昂首巨马，奋蹄于星斗山、云雾山中。团堡海拔在500 ～1500米之间，位于群山环抱的高原盆地，云腾雾绕，气象万千。生产过程为全程无菌操作，公司产品主要出口日韩欧美等。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20141124/20141124010311_65939.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141124/20141124010311_65939.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp;硒品汇所售有机脱水生山药片为</span></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5;\">绿色食品,健康食品，食用方便，200克一盒，包装精美，无论自用还是送人，都是好选择。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141124/20141124003235_96398.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20141124/20141124003235_96398.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201610/thumb_img/29_thumb_G_1475877890359.jpg', 'images/201610/goods_img/29_G_1475877890086.jpg', 'images/201610/source_img/29_G_1475877890544.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1475877890', '100', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1475877892', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
