s_desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><img title=\"硒虫草,有机硒,富硒产品\" alt=\"硒虫草,有机硒,富硒产品\" width=\"750\" height=\"469\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809105859_91240.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809105859_91240.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 28px; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"750\" height=\"84\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809122221_41915.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809122221_41915.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><img title=\"圣峰硒虫草,湖北恩施,高硒\" alt=\"圣峰硒虫草,湖北恩施,高硒\" width=\"750\" height=\"562\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809112501_33059.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809112501_33059.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 硒虫草主要为富硒虫草花，<span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">&ldquo;虫草花&rdquo;并非花，它是人工培养的虫草子实体，</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">虫草花是北冬虫草的简称，也叫</span>蛹虫草<span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">或蛹草，俗名不老草，是虫，菌结合的药用真菌，现代稀有的中草药。虫草花外观上最大的特点是没有了&ldquo;虫体&rdquo;，而只有橙色或者黄色的&ldquo;草&rdquo;，其头部的子实体，这是其有效成分最集中的地方。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">虫草花的菌种来源于蛹虫草，它们存在着许多相似之处。测定结果显示，人工培植的蛹虫草子实体，虫草素、虫草酸、虫草多糖以及氨基酸、维生素、微量元素等成分与冬虫夏草、蛹虫草的含量相似。现在很多应用上</span><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">把蛹虫草作冬虫夏草的代用品使用。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 14px;\">口感不错，具有独特的香味，味道鲜美</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809133634_15854.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809133634_15854.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img title=\"无菌培育,恩施富硒,武陵山区\" alt=\"无菌培育,恩施富硒,武陵山区\" width=\"750\" height=\"579\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809113519_13451.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809113519_13451.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809113541_49895.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809113541_49895.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130812/20130812111909_24259.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130812/20130812111909_24259.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;硒品汇所售的硒虫草，是</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">选用聚硒能力特别强的北冬虫夏草菌种，利用恩施天然硒资源作为培养基的硒源，采用现代生物组培技术，经反复驯化与生物转换，使无机硒通过虫草菌的分解、吸收、转化成易被人体利用的有机硒，使虫草的有效成份与有机硒的功效相结合，从而发挥更好的生物学作用。</span><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809113958_11404.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130809/20130809113958_11404.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;硒品汇该款硒虫草为80G精包装礼盒，每盒里面有2个铁盒。每个铁盒里面为2g/袋*20.硒虫草属补硒养生品，是人们日常补硒、养生、滋补之珍品。药食同源，无毒副作用，四季皆宜。不管是自用还是送礼，都是佳的选择。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805165022_15337.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805165022_15337.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;硒<span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">草花含有丰富的</span>蛋白质<span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">、18种氨基酸、17种微量元素、12种维生素： A、B1、B2、B6、B12、C、D、E等含量高于菇类。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">硒虫草的有效成分主要为腺苷、虫草素、虫草酸、和虫草多糖，<strong>特别是硒与蛋白质、氨基酸的有机结合，对虫草的生物学功能和药理学作用产生了若干倍放大作用。</strong>硒虫草的虫草素含量是野生虫草的35-89.3倍、腺嘌呤高出5-40倍，腺苷是野生虫草的4.2-6.77倍、SOD比活性高出4.11倍。在18种氨基酸中有13种氨基酸含量比野生虫草高出111-229%，硒的含量是野生虫草的100倍以上，有4种营养成分是野生虫草所没有的，其营养价值大大高于野生虫草。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">中科院北京理化测试中心和谱尼测试科技检测显示，野生虫草、人工虫草与硒虫草比较，三者在有机和无机营养成分种类上基本一致，但在主要功能成分含量上硒虫草分别高于人工虫草和天然虫草几倍到一百倍。具体数据为：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; ▼</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">尚灵牌硒虫草腺苷的含量是野生虫草的5倍！</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;▼尚灵牌硒虫草虫草素的含量是野生虫草的30&mdash;50倍！</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;▼尚灵牌硒硒的含量是野生虫草的100倍！</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;▼尚灵牌硒虫草其他有效成分与野生虫草的有效成分均在一个数量值上！</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 21pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807141208_57056.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807141208_57056.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 虫草花是一种颇受欢迎的食材，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">含硒的虫草现在可以天天吃，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">多用于作冲印，</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">泡酒，汤料和药膳，是药膳中的新宠，备受医生、营养师、厨师和家庭主妇的青睐。<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\"><strong>建</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\"><strong>议每人每次用量2-4克。保健或调理用量加倍，每人每次不超过20克为佳。</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\"><strong>冲饮：</strong></span>将硒虫草如茶叶般冲泡一次或多次，之后将硒虫草细嚼吃下。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">泡酒：</span></strong>将50-100克硒虫草置入普通白酒1-5公斤内，待颜色泛黄时即可饮用。每人每次用量建议不超过100克。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\"><strong>煮汤：</strong></span>煮汤时温度过高会损失营养成分，<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">待关火后温度下降至70&deg;左右时，将硒虫草放入并淹没其中，</span>待温度适宜食用时即可。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px; font-size: 14px;\"><b>硒虫草炖瘦肉</b><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">原料】<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">硒</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">虫草5g、元肉3g、淮山5g、芡实10g、瘦肉100g</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">这是一个人食用的分量，将原料置于炖盅隔水蒸或炖即可。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><strong>硒虫草神仙粥</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">&nbsp; &nbsp;【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">原料】<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">硒</span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">虫草4g、人参3克，茯苓3克，麦门冬3克，黑米80克，北糖15克</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">&nbsp; &nbsp;【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">按一般煲粥方法即可。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><strong>硒虫草蒸母鸭</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【原料】</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">嫩母鸭1只，约重1500克，硒虫草18克，料酒，葱、姜、盐适量</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\">将鸭洗净，将硒虫草塞入鸭腹内，放入锅里加入姜、料酒。停火十分钟后加适量盐、吃肉饮汁</span>。</span></p>\r\n<div><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201610/thumb_img/30_thumb_G_1475878267005.jpg', 'images/201610/goods_img/30_G_1475878267258.jpg', 'images/201610/source_img/30_G_1475878267850.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '24', '1475878267', '100', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1475878553', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
