0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; width: 750px;\"><br />\r\n<div class=\"goods_desc\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img title=\"黑木耳,清血脂,血管清道夫,秋耳,\" alt=\"黑木耳,清血脂,血管清道夫,秋耳,\" width=\"750\" height=\"412\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807163322_10134.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807163322_10134.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807163517_89809.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807163517_89809.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img title=\"有机木耳,富硒木耳,东北黑木耳,有机认证木耳,\" alt=\"有机木耳,富硒木耳,东北黑木耳,有机认证木耳,\" width=\"750\" height=\"446\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807163455_75127.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807163455_75127.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">硒品汇所售的该款木耳为有机木耳</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">，耳片乌黑光润，背面呈灰白色，片大均匀，耳瓣舒展，体轻干燥，半透明，胀性好，无杂质，有清香气味。表面黑而光润，有一面呈灰色，手摸上去感觉干燥，新鲜时软，干后成角质。口感细嫩，风味特殊，嘴尝无异味。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">硒品汇富硒木耳泡发率非常好，<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">泡发比一般都在1：13-15左右</span>，吃起来非常爽口，肉质厚感，营养也是其他木耳的几倍。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img title=\"恩施风景,神秘的北纬30度,油菜化开,,\" alt=\"恩施风景,神秘的北纬30度,油菜化开,,\" width=\"769\" height=\"1605\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805163123_71556.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805163123_71556.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 湖北恩施</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">森林覆盖率高达</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">70%</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">以上，有&ldquo;鄂西林海&rdquo;的美誉，林木资源丰富，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">毗邻神龙架，地处武夷山脉，海拔高，</span><span style=\"line-height: 24px; font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">属于亚热带山原型季风性湿润气候。其特点是光热充足、雨量充沛、春夏多雨、秋冬干旱、无霜期长、冬无严寒、四季湿和，小气候明显，昼夜温差大，地处偏僻，无任何工业污染。该地为独立硒矿床及富硒生态圈，突然中富含优质硒资源，该地的深山老林中盛产各种野生山珍和药材。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><img title=\"木耳礼盒,含硒木耳,盒装秋耳,干货礼盒,\" alt=\"木耳礼盒,含硒木耳,盒装秋耳,干货礼盒,\" width=\"750\" height=\"1028\" original=\"/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807163342_33280.jpg\" src=\"http://www.xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807163342_33280.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;硒品汇所售的有机黑木耳</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">为纸盒礼盒装，有有机认证标识和防伪条形码，便于追溯产品的生产源头，保证食品质量，同时天然富含有机硒。内包装为为透明塑料袋包装，简易拉链式封口，便于取用和保存。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805165022_15337.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130805/20130805165022_15337.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;富硒有机黑木耳</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">100</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克干黑木耳中水分</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">10.9</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克、蛋白质</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">10.6</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克、脂肪</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">0.2</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克、碳水化合物</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">65.5</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克、热量</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">306</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">千卡、粗纤维</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">7.0</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克、灰分</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">5.8</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克、钙</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">357</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">毫克、磷</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">201</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">毫克、铁</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">185</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">毫克、胡萝卜素</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">毫克、硫胺素</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">0.15</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">毫克、核黄素</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">0.55</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">毫克、烟碱酸</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">2.7</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">毫克和硒等无机盐，它还含有甘露聚糖、甘露糖、葡萄糖、木糖、葡萄糖醛酸等碳水化合物以及卵磷脂、脑磷脂、鞘磷酸等重要的有机化合物。黑木耳的钙是一般肉类的</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">－</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">40</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">倍，是牛奶的</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">2.3</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">倍。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 21pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" original=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807141208_57056.jpg\" src=\"http://xipinhui.cn/images/upload/image/20130807/20130807141208_57056.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; margin-top: 5px;\" /></div>\r\n<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>【烹饪指导】：</strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;木耳最营养的吃法&mdash;&mdash;生拌：</span></strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">直接把木耳用冷水泡发，然后加上调料凉拌就行了。注意</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">：泡发木耳最好不要超过</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">24</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">个小时，这样可以减少营养素溶于水中的损失。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">泡发后还要用清水多洗几次。如果不习惯吃生拌的，可以将木耳泡发好后，用沸水迅速焯一下再拌。</span></p>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;此外，木耳还可以炒食，做汤等多种食用方法。</span>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><b><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">木耳炒腐竹</span></b></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">原料】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">腐竹</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">150</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">克，黑木耳50g</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">，蒜</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">瓣，姜</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">4</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">片，调味料：</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">配料】</span><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">盐，生抽酱油，糖，胡椒粉，鸡精</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">黑木耳泡发，腐竹用水泡软切段，蒜切片，腐竹放入开水锅煮一分钟，捞出控水，炒锅加油烧热，下蒜和姜片爆香，加腐竹翻炒一会，加黑木耳，盐，糖，生抽，胡椒粉，鸡精炒匀即可。</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>双耳汤</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;【原料】</span>木耳、银耳各10克 冰糖30克</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;【做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">将木耳、银耳用温水泡发</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">(</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">木耳若太大块，可撕成小块），拣去蒂及杂质，洗净放锅内；</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">加清水</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">3</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">杯煮沸后，用小火煮</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">小时，加入冰糖即可</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>木耳炒肚片</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【材料】</span>猪肚500克，水发木耳150克，蒜50克，食油50克，盐、黄酒、白糖、酱油、姜、醋、味精、水淀粉各少许</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">【做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">用醋和盐反复擦洗猪肚，再用清水洗净，放人沸水内煮至八成熟捞出，用刀斜切成片；蒜切片，姜切末；</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">炒锅置旺火上，加油烧热，用姜末炸锅，加入蒜、木耳、肚片炒下，随后加黄油、盐、白糖、酱油，加适量水烧开，用水淀粉勾芡，加入味精拌一拌即可。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>清炖木耳香菇</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;【原料】</span>水发木耳300克，香菇8个，葱、姜、黄酒、盐、熟油各适量</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 15.75pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 51, 51);\">&nbsp;【做法】</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 14px;\">将香菇用冷水泡发，洗净，用调料拌匀，倒人煮沸的骨汤内，文火炖15分钟，起锅后加入味精和胡椒即成。</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'images/201610/thumb_img/31_thumb_G_1475974524675.jpg', 'images/201610/goods_img/31_G_1475974524378.jpg', 'images/201610/source_img/31_G_1475974524569.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1475974524', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '1475974740', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '');
